{"tid":1955372,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有學生組織真係好希望有手足可以幫幫手 求下有心人幫推","createTime":"2020-04-02T12:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T19:49:13.000Z","uid":153864,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"212f55f23ad7fccd09a4d1337a53f9ee498b21b1","tid":1955372,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLVOZz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLVOZz.jpg&h=b8e9f305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B-ehSkQn3pg/?igshid=141j05wiaihni\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB-ehSkQn3pg%2F%3Figshid%3D141j05wiaihni&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=0d883209\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB-ehSkQn3pg%2F%3Figshid%3D141j05wiaihni&h=130fa40b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B-ehSkQn3pg/?igshid=141j05wiaihni</a><br />\n<br />\n［香港思流營運贊助］<br />\n-<br />\n香港思流的財務報表已公布於上一個post，現公開希望得到有心人的捐助，以助組織營運及籌備更多活動。🙇🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n-<br />\n🤔你地之前用「中學生反修例關注組」嘅名義收過錢喎？D錢去晒邊？係咪人血？<br />\n-<br />\n💡該次徵收捐款作營運資金共收到了$2900.00。組織轉型後，所有資金已經撥入香港思流（轉型後）。<br />\n💡派口罩活動用左$3000+，overdraft嘅錢由成員夾錢自行負擔。我地定時會公佈財政報告，以悉除公眾疑慮。<br />\n-<br />\n🤔你地黎緊仲會唔會徵收捐助架？我想支持你地<br />\n-<br />\n💡會嘅，其實我地一直都希望可以得到大家嘅支持。<br />\n💡有能力嘅手足可以係金錢上資助我地嘅營運資金（包括購買物資派發，枱，街站的物資以及倉務等），亦可以捐助物資以視支持（例如音響器材「mic箱」🎤，枱，櫈等街站物資）。<br />\n💡負擔唔起資金我地組織嘅手足只要follow我地嘅page，share我地嘅post同埋係我地嘅post下面留言已經好足夠💙<br />\n-<br />\n🤔想捐助物資/營運資金比香港思流🙋🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n💡請dm我地查詢🙇🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n-<br />\n我地非常一需要有心人嘅捐助，以支持組織的活動🙇🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n#香港思流 #捐贈 #中學生 <br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇佢地呢個組織好似好後期先開始<br />\n佢地前身係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n中學生反修例關注組<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n佢地係6月9日已經有投身呢一次運動<br />\n係6 7 8月更係有<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n無間斷開物資/傳單街站<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n（<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BzOdR-6Hlcp/?igshid=1la135xyofysm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBzOdR-6Hlcp%2F%3Figshid%3D1la135xyofysm&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=bfcc106d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBzOdR-6Hlcp%2F%3Figshid%3D1la135xyofysm&h=5c881ee5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BzOdR-6Hlcp/?igshid=1la135xyofysm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BzpSwg7HOYU/?igshid=evkgnmzx4n8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBzpSwg7HOYU%2F%3Figshid%3Devkgnmzx4n8&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=7e041c15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBzpSwg7HOYU%2F%3Figshid%3Devkgnmzx4n8&h=572f88dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BzpSwg7HOYU/?igshid=evkgnmzx4n8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bzu0rvqnooO/?igshid=1v03ou8l5hir\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBzu0rvqnooO%2F%3Figshid%3D1v03ou8l5hir&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=edb671e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBzu0rvqnooO%2F%3Figshid%3D1v03ou8l5hir&h=2eea9d33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Bzu0rvqnooO/?igshid=1v03ou8l5hir</a> 仲有好多好多）<br />\n<br />\n如果有心人可唔可以幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢班中學生真係好有心架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1正皮=1支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1caae3eadb67ef3df082f6736bbc54d31925d9c","tid":1955372,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi